text: Komintern () is a rural locality (a village) in Rayevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 36 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Davlekanovo, 5 km from Rayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Komintern, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
